'''''Applied Energy''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering research on [[energy engineering]] that was established in 1975. It is published by [[Elsevier]] and the [[editor-in-chief]] is Jinyue Yan. According to the ''[[Journal Citation Reports]]'', the journal has a 2014 [[impact factor]] of  5.613, ranking it 9th out of 89 journals in the category "Energy & Fuels" and 6th out of 135 journals in "engineering, chemical".<ref>[[Thomson Reuters]], Journal Citation Reports 2015, Retrieved 27. December 2015.</ref>

