The '''content industry''' is an [[umbrella term]] that encompasses companies owning and providing [[mass media]] and media metadata. This can include [[music]] and [[Film|movies]], text publications of any kind, ownership of [[standardization|standards]], [[geographic data]], and metadata about all and any of the above.

In the [[Information Age]], the content industry comprises an enormous [[Market (economics)|market]].

